	(lib_symbols)
	(text "CLOCKING  +  WORD-CLOCK INPUT
Components:
 - J: 75ohm PCB BNC -> 75R term -> AC-couple+bias
 - U: TLV3501 comparator -> WCLK_CMOS (3V3)   [D7]
 - U: CS2000CP-CZZ clock gen (I2C: SDA/SCL)
      CLK_IN <- WCLK_CMOS ; REF_CLK <- Y 24.576MHz xtal
      CLK_OUT -> MCLK (256*Fs)
 - Y: 24.576 MHz crystal (REF_CLK timebase)
Outputs: MCLK -> Digital/AES ; WCLK_MON + CS2K_UNLK -> MCU
Powered from +3V3_CLK (clean)."
